<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Billings, Dorothy L., 72, of Palmdale, assistant manager for Thousand Elms 
Mobile Home Park. Chapel of the Valley Mortuary, Palmdale.  
</P>
<P>
 Bruha, Mathilda, 103, of Burbank, homemaker.The Valley Funeral Home, Burbank.  
</P>
<P>
 Carter, Noble, 73, of Van Nuys, retired supervisor for Lockheed Corp. Forest 
Lawn Mortuary, Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Espinosa, Raul Jose (Sirongie) Sr., 55, of Arleta, cabinetmaker. Noble Chapel, 
San Fernando. 
</P>
