<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020194-0116 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 009113 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 1, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
