<P>
REGIONAL ROUNDUP: UNILAB COMPLETES PREMIER ACQUISITION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Unilab Corp., a Tarzana-based provider of clinical laboratory testing 
services, said it completed the previously announced acquisition of Premier 
Laboratory Services Inc. for $31.5 million in cash and $7.5 million in Unilab 
common stock. 
</P>
<P>
 San Jose-based PathLab, the operating unit of Premier, has annual sales of 
about $22 million, Unilab said. Unilab has facilities in Los Angeles, San Jose 
and Sacramento, and in Europe. 
</P>
</TEXT>
