<P>
 Randy Eason scored 30 points, 21 in the first half, to lead College of the 
Canyons to a 77-67 Western State Conference victory over host Glendale. Canyons 
(8-15, 2-1 in conference play) led by two with 40 seconds left but padded the 
lead on free throws. 
</P>
<P>
 Mike Wright led Glendale (11-12, 2-2) with 24 points. 
</P>
<P>
 In other men's basketball games: 
</P>
<P>
