 Camarillo 79, Channel Islands 50 -- Jim Hansen scored 15 points and grabbed 10 
rebounds to lead the Scorpions in a Marmonte League game. Andrew Richards of 
Camarillo (10-10, 6-4) led all scorers with 16 points. 
