ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: BUENA PARK; SUPERVISOR TO SPEAK AT TOWN HALL MEETING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Residents are invited to meet Orange County Supervisor William G. Steiner, 
whose 4th District includes Buena Park, at a town hall meeting today. 
</P>
<P>
 The meeting will be held from 7 to 8 p.m. in the City Council chambers, 6650 
Beach Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
 Steiner, who was appointed to serve on the Board of Supervisors last spring, 
will address county issues that affect Buena Park. He will also answer 
questions. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information about the meeting, call (714) 834-3440. 
