<DOCNO> LA020194-0485 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 009482 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 1, 1994, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 10; Column 1; Metro Desk 
