<HEADLINE>
<P>
TECHNOLOGY: MARKETING DIGITAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Dean Takahashi, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ingram Micro Inc. in Santa Ana will distribute the entire personal computer 
line of Digital Equipment Corp. starting immediately. 
</P>
<P>
 Digital is expanding its reach beyond the corporate marketplace to individual 
and small-business computer users and so needs a distributor that can put it in 
touch with new markets, said Harry Copperman, vice president of Digital's 
PersonalComputer Business Unit. 
</P>
</TEXT>
